attributionInfo.brokerName: Rhonda Silver Real Estate Group LLC

data.description: cozy and quiet 3-bedroom 2 bath home on 1.78 acres. Conveniently located close to Walmart and Interstate 40. Thru the front door you will walk into a nice foyer with beautiful round archways, leading you into the large open living room with gas log fireplace. To your left you will find 2 good sized bedrooms and then a share bath. Go down the hall and it takes you to your Oversized primary bedroom with private entrance, walk in closet and the second bathroom. There is a Covered front porch for relaxing and grilling, and a fenced in yard for dogs or kids to play. Large field in the back that is currently being cut for hay but could be used for a big garden or to build your swimming pool. It also has a 1 car garage or workshop around the back of the house and a circle drive for easy entry. All of this within close proximity to Asheville or Hickory and the growing town of Marion. Call today to see it before its gone!
